data.description: Located in beautiful, safe neighborhood! Oakwood floors throughout the house, tile in bathroom and kitchen. All rooms have fans and double pane windows. Recently painted inside. 2 wall gas heaters. 1 Room walk-in closet with vanity desk. Upgraded electrical panel and outside plumbing. Tankless water heater! Garage being used as family room and office (possible attic storage as well)! Big 4 car driveway. Large lot with spacious backyard. Large storage shed. Home located close to freeway and shopping malls. You will love this home!
